      <hedline>
        <hl1>EXECUTIVE CHANGES</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>GENERAL ELECTRIC CO., Fairfield, Conn., named Mark Begor chief financial officer of its NBC television network unit effective immediately, succeeding Warren Jenson, who is leaving to become chief financial officer of Delta Air Lines Inc.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>GENERAL ELECTRIC CO., Fairfield, Conn., named Mark Begor chief financial officer of its NBC television network unit effective immediately, succeeding Warren Jenson, who is leaving to become chief financial officer of Delta Air Lines Inc.</p>
        <p>PATRIOT AMERICAN HOSPITALITY INC., Dallas, said its chief financial officer, Rex E. Stewart, would resign next month.</p>
      </block>
